@End Reasoning
Process called "parse_expression" takes parser as Integer returns Integer:
    Return proc parse_logical_or with parser
End Process

@Reasoning:
Lowest-precedence binary level — left-associative '|' (element-wise OR) and
'||' (short-circuit OR). Distinguishing the two at AST construction time
preserves the user's semantic intent for codegen (short-circuit must not
evaluate the RHS when the LHS is true).
